 FoodRecipe App

A React Native mobile application built with Expo for discovering, saving, and cooking delicious recipes.

## Project Overview
FoodRecipe App is designed for home cooks, students, and food enthusiasts. It allows users to explore a wide variety of recipes, filter them by category, save favorites, and view complete cooking instructions.

## Key Features
- **12+ Recipe Categories**: Italian, Indian, Salad, Dessert, Mexican, Asian, Breakfast, Vegetarian, Seafood, BBQ & Grill, Healthy, Quick & Easy  
- **Recipe Details**: Ingredients, instructions, preparation time, number of servings, calories, and difficulty level  
- **Category Filtering**: Click a category to see recipes specific to it  
- **Favorites**: Heart icon toggles favoriting; saved recipes appear in a dedicated section  
- **Recipe Modal**: Detailed view of recipes with images and step-by-step instructions  

